## **2. Register for an event**

Volunteers can browse the events and then register themselves for the events that they want to volunteer for.

*you need to login as a **volunteer** in order to register for an event.

[Login as volunteer to View/book Events](https://voluntia.herokuapp.com/login)

Steps for Booking:

1. Go to the event page and view it details.

2. Click on “Book now” button to register.

3. You will be redirected to the dashboard.

4. The event will be then added to the pending list of events.

5. After the organization approves your request for participation you then are successfully booked for an event.

6. You can now see the event in confirmed events list.

